name: Eye-ray-ser Dungeon
description:
Jump to the goal and dodge the eye rays, or use them to destroy obstacles. Careful, as the eye ray's will erase any platform they hit. Complete all 10 levels and then face off against the final Eye-ray-ser boss. 

Music assets used from The Toadz: 

https://thetoadz.com/album/the-royalty-free-collection
